name: BirdChain
description: Birdchain is base in the era of sharing Economy allowing users to benefit greatly by using blockchain technology. Birdchain has multiple products such as DEFI, NFT etc. Birdchain has currently built an incentivised App for the sharing economy era. It revolves around an easy-to-use, high engagement, marketing & content platform where users engage with content and get rewarded. we are working to add more usecase to the token. such as incentivize users for liquidity provision to the Birdchainswap defi platform.
